[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1337","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1337.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1115","title":"HP Apollo Domain/OS /etc/suid_exec 权限提升漏洞","description":"HP Apollo Domain/OS 操作系统的 /etc/suid_exec 程序存在安全漏洞，该程序与 Korn Shell (ksh) 相关，由于未正确限制 suid 权限，本地攻击者可通过执行特制的 suid_exec 程序提升至 root 权限。该漏洞影响 sr10.2 及 sr10.3 beta 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限方可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1115"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1990-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:45.133","remediation":"建议立即升级 HP Apollo Domain/OS 至 sr10.4 或更高版本，该版本已修复 /etc/suid_exec 中 Korn Shell (ksh) 相关的权限提升漏洞。如无法升级，建议移除 /etc/suid_exec 程序的 SUID 位（chmod u-s /etc/suid_exec），并限制可执行该程序的用户范围。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1990-04.html","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/a-30.shtml","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/6721.php","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/7","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/1999/CVE-1999-1115.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a662dc905cd549a2105daacbfce64cf01652761d/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1115.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1115","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/263f37bc67cd24fe03a39077d8b57f3001369a95/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1115.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1115.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/bf2339193e1c10dc2db330718adeb8cc8d88c4dd/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-m52q-cq5w-w8r4/GHSA-m52q-cq5w-w8r4.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154700_154800.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1115.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--63572ced-8268-4516-9b19-a4143c8172ca.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1115.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1337.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1387","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1387.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1197","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9124,\"outputTokens\":18,\"totalTokens\":10806}}","description":"SunOS 4.1.1 中的 TIOCCONS 接口未正确校验用户权限，本地用户可通过重定向控制台输入输出实现权限提升。该漏洞影响 SunOS 4.1.1 系统，需本地用户权限即可利用，攻击者可通过恶意重定向控制台输入输出获取提升权限，CVSS 评分 7.2，属于高危本地提权漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1197"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1990-12-20T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:55.497","remediation":"升级到 SunOS 4.1.3 或更高版本（或迁移至 Solaris 2.x 系列），该版本已修复 TIOCCONS 权限检查缺陷。如无法立即升级，可通过停用 /dev/console 重定向功能、限制普通用户对 /dev/console 的访问权限，并将控制台访问限制在受信任的 tty 设备上作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1990-12.html","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7140.php","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/14","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/1999/CVE-1999-1197.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8f7915616bad1c7280e28216588ab0258074928/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1197.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1197","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/ea13d8ca97b52327fe351b64da51866911834231/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1197.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1197.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/424512debdca84cc53ffa1fb3810a74f7b1905a5/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5w36-3rq9-chgj/GHSA-5w36-3rq9-chgj.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154700_154800.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1197.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000009.txt","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1387.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1311","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1311.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1057","title":"VMS ANALYZE/PROCESS_DUMP 命令本地权限提升漏洞","description":"VMS 4.0 至 5.3 版本中的 ANALYZE/PROCESS_DUMP DCL 命令存在权限提升漏洞，本地用户可通过执行该命令获取超出自身权限的系统访问权限。该漏洞源于系统对 DCL 命令的权限检查不充分，导致低权限用户能够利用 ANALYZE/PROCESS_DUMP 功能以更高权限执行操作，进而完全控制受影响的 VMS 系统。攻击者需要拥有本地系统访问权限才能利用此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1057"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1990-10-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:36.917","remediation":"升级到 VMS 5.4 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，可通过设置 ANALYZE 命令的 ACL 权限，仅允许授权管理员执行 ANALYZE/PROCESS_DUMP，限制普通用户调用该命令以提升权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/b-04.shtml","http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1990-07.html","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7137.php","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/12","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/1999/CVE-1999-1057.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/42b5b7a8a9b34b1b292b9bfd27242e499ccb6cb9/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1057.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1057","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/21d84550d4f5d6b78cac9f7c41b1b20a874c9f15/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1057.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1057.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d94ad47d0f2016e121b6d251f490e890714f8916/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q5xx-4g5h-3h6c/GHSA-q5xx-4g5h-3h6c.json","https://github.com/Stallion77RepoOfficial/PoC-Repo/blob/d208666140ed89c18899b79ea93d18444fc164de/1999/1999-1057.py","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154700_154800.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1057.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1057.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1311.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0199","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0199.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0084","title":"多款 NFS 服务器权限提升漏洞","description":"某些 NFS 服务器存在权限提升漏洞，由于未对 `mknod` 系统调用进行有效的权限检查，普通用户可通过 `mknod` 创建可写的 `/dev/kmem` 设备文件，并将自身 UID 设置为 0（root），从而获得内核内存的读写访问权限，实现本地权限提升至 root。该漏洞影响多个 NFS 服务实现，攻击者需拥有本地用户账户，CVSS 评分 8.4，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":8.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0084"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1990-05-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:32.553","remediation":"升级至 NFS v4.1.3 或更高版本以修复 mknod 权限提升漏洞。在客户端挂载 NFS 共享时务必使用 `nosuid` 和 `nodev` 选项，禁止设备文件创建和 SUID 可执行；服务端导出目录时启用 `root_squash` 将 root 用户映射为匿名用户，并严格限制 exports 权限为只读（`ro`）而非读写（`rw`），同时移除不必要的 writable kmem 设备访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/78"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0199.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0195","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0195.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0082","title":"FTPD CWD ~root 命令权限提升漏洞","description":"FTP 守护进程（ftpd）在处理 CWD（Change Working Directory）命令时存在路径遍历缺陷，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过发送特制的 `CWD ~root` 指令将当前工作目录切换至 root 用户家目录，从而绕过文件访问限制获取超级用户权限，实现对目标服务器的完全控制。该漏洞无需任何认证即可远程触发，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0082"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1988-11-11T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:32.300","remediation":"升级 ftpd 至厂商最后发布的修复版本（如 wu-ftpd 2.6.2+、ProFTPD 1.2.0rc2+），禁用匿名用户的 CWD 命令或限制 `~root` 路径解析；如无法升级，关闭 FTP 服务并迁移至 SFTP/SCP 替代。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.alw.nih.gov/Security/Docs/admin-guide-to-cracking.101.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0195.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0223","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0223.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0095","title":"Berkeley Sendmail Debug 命令远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Sendmail 5.58 及更早版本中默认启用了调试（debug）命令功能，远程攻击者可通过 SMTP 端口向目标发送特制的 debug 命令，以 root 权限执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响广泛部署的 Berkeley Sendmail 邮件服务器，无需身份认证即可远程利用，危害等级严重。厂商已发布补丁禁用调试功能。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0095"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1988-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:34.460","remediation":"立即将 Sendmail 升级至 8.6.x 或更高版本，该系列已默认禁用 debug/wizard 调试命令。如无法升级，在 sendmail.cf 配置文件中添加 Ow 选项（即 O Wizard=no）以关闭 wiz 模式。在网络层面限制对 TCP 端口 25 的访问，仅允许可信来源连接 SMTP 服务作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://seclists.org/fulldisclosure/2019/Jun/16","http://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2019/06/05/4","http://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2019/06/06/1","http://www.osvdb.org/195","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19028","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0095.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0095.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0095","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/1999/CVE-1999-0095.rules","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0095.json","https://github.com/Mishthi27/SentrySense2.0/blob/de64bcf93503f6469484cdfdd5c26732e8f3f623/predictive_ai/threats/CVE-1999-0095.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0095.json","https://github.com/trailofbits/cb-multios/blob/810d7b24b1f62f56ef49b148fe155b0d0629cad2/challenges/REMATCH_1--Hat_Trick--Morris_Worm/README.md","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/663.txt","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0095.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0223.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1347","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1347.toml","cve_id":"无","title":"1Panel面板最新前台RCE漏洞","description":"1Panel 1Panel面板最新前台RCE漏洞 RCE - GET / HTTP/1.1 Host: 192.168.99.6 User-Agent: ua&#x27;, &#x27;blog.mo60.cn&#x27;, 5201314, &#x27;&#x27;, &#x27;&#x27;, 1, &#x27;2024-06-09 08:16:52&#x27;, 1817921010.847, &#x27;/AAAAAAA&#x27;, 52014, &#x27;2025-06-09&#x27;, &#x27;16&#x27;, &#x27;&#x27;, &#x27;&#x27;, &#x27;Linux&#x27;, &#x27;edge&#x27;, &#x27;pc&#x27;, &#x27;&#x27;, &#x27;&#x27;);ATTACH DATABASE &#x27;/www/sites/index/index/mo60.cn.php&#x27; AS test ;create TABLE test.exp (dataz text) ; insert INTO test.exp (dataz) VALUES (&#x27;&lt;?= md5(&quot;blog.mo60.cn&quot;); ?&gt;&#x27;);#","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["HWPOC-2024-04a65f18"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"","updated":"","remediation":"请参考官方安全公告，及时安装安全更新或升级到最新版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T02:52:04.305373996+00:00","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1347.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1325","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1325.toml","cve_id":"无","title":"瑞友天翼应用虚拟化系统 反序列化远程代码执行漏洞","description":"瑞友天翼应用虚拟化系统存在反序列化注入漏洞，攻击者可通过向 `/ConsoleExternalUploadApi.XGI` 接口发送特制的 POST 请求，利用参数注入触发反序列化操作，从而在目标服务器上执行任意代码并获取系统控制权。该漏洞无需身份认证即可远程利用，攻击门槛低，影响部署了瑞友天翼应用虚拟化系统的服务器，可导致服务器被完全控制、数据泄露等严重后果。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["HWPOC-2024-03d8fca4"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"0812","updated":"0812","remediation":"立即联系瑞友官方获取最新安全补丁，升级瑞友天翼应用虚拟化系统至最新版本。如无法立即升级，可在 Web 应用防火墙（WAF）或反向代理层面添加规则，拦截对 /ConsoleExternalUploadApi.XGI 接口的异常 POST 请求，特别是过滤 key、initParams、sign 等参数中包含的反序列化攻击载荷。同时建议限制管理后台的访问 IP 白名单，避免将 ConsoleExternalUploadApi 接口暴露在公网。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1325.toml"}]